## What you need to modify

Your project has 13 files. You only need to care about 4:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `src/App.tsx` | Your main app component | **Every time** |
| `src/pages/Home.tsx` | Your pages | **Every time** |
| `tests/app.test.tsx` | Tests for your components | **Every time** |
| `src/main.tsx` | Entry point, router + query setup | Rarely |
| Others (vite config, eslint, Docker, CI) | Project infrastructure | Almost never |

## Quick Start

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173).

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start dev server with HMR |
| `npm run build` | Type-check and build for production |
| `npm run preview` | Preview production build locally |
| `npm test` | Run tests once (Vitest) |
| `npm run test:watch` | Run tests in watch mode |
| `npm run lint` | Lint source with ESLint |

## Project Structure

```
├── src/
│   ├── main.tsx           # Entry point (TanStack Query + Router)
